name: GASMANSN.WAD (Gas Mansion DeathMatch)
description: Gas Mansion Deathmatch! This deathmatch takes place in one of the wings of the legendary Gas Mansion. The setting is tailored for very fast action with cool places to lurk and devious traps to surprise your enemy with! You will certainly enjoy hours of quality kills in Gas Mansion! Watch for the cool dropping staircase! Keep on the lookout for a new single/co-op set of levels to go along with this deathmatch!
